==English==

===Etymology===
From [[Sinhalese]], reduplication of [[beri]], ''weakness''.

===Alternative spellings===
* [[beri-beri]]

===Noun===
'''beriberi''' (''uncountable'')

# {{pathology}} an [[ailment]] caused by a deficiency of [[thiamine]] (vitamin B1)

====Synonyms====
*[[endemic neuritis]]
*[[kakke]]

====Derived terms====
*[[dry beriberi]]
*[[wet beriberi]]

